document_data.name: Westlight Walk
document_data.mainbody: '''Westlight Walk''' was a small street found in the city of [[Westgate]].
document_data.Location: Westlight Walk was found in the north or northwest section of the city, branching from [[Westgate Market Street]] and terminating north of the harbor.
